vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting an MU-1 Mixed Use District and a resolution accepting deed restrictions volunteered by the applicant on property zoned an IR Industrial Research District, on the west line of Dennis Road at the terminus of Sundial Drive, between Northaven Road and Satsuma Drive
Recommendation of Staff: Approval, subject to deed restrictions volunteered by the applicant
Recommendation of CPC: Approval, subject to deed restrictions volunteered by the applicant
Z212-331(JM)
